{"tid":426102,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"收工遇到啲咁既事","createTime":"2017-10-06T10:19:10.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-06T11:13:55.000Z","uid":112380,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"ffb3eaac3e0c5af47eafd1fecea93b5ac6cb054f","tid":426102,"uid":112380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T10:19:10.000Z","msg":"岩岩係元朗收工<br />\n行緊天橋既時候<br />\n有個來自桂拜既男人拎左張報失紙<br />\n同我講唔見左銀包 3800港紙 手機<br />\n話依家好肚餓 又無人識英文（我英文好屎）<br />\n最後比左100佢食野<br />\n<br />\n唔知係騙子定咩 <br />\n最後我都幫左佢 佢仲問我拎電話 話洗唔洗比返錢我<br />\n我答左佢唔洗 就走左人<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nSorry for 19999"},{"pid":"8930b755cff2f0da5df4d6eec45e7af89f944c27","tid":426102,"uid":235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T10:20:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d04f9230a29210f38d68aa340f95039cff550425","tid":426102,"uid":101882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T10:25:37.000Z","msg":"見到呢啲事最好買野食比佢"},{"pid":"eef5dd70f548b3b458c5c7cb764747acfcb245f8","tid":426102,"uid":53798,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T10:26:54.000Z","msg":"100%比人呃"},{"pid":"51bcfa251dbcc218b77d2de898ab17b9eebd6919","tid":426102,"uid":85819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T10:27:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3e052afe1a3b9b7f2699ef3c987d8eb5253e319e","tid":426102,"uid":112380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T10:35:14.000Z","msg":"借完比佢 佢伸隻手黎 握手 <br />\n到落天橋 佢揮手同我講bye<br />\n都係同情心 當幫左佢<br />\n下次見到都當乜都唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e78a79f1e82954fa7fa7c7dc059d8bf3ffca029","tid":426102,"uid":74990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T10:37:00.000Z","msg":"on9"},{"pid":"5a505cd56e3ee289ce64e7fe553af46897346035","tid":426102,"uid":73856,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T10:41:22.000Z","msg":"on99"},{"pid